<span class="displaytext">santa fe, nm-- new mexico governor and presidential candidate (candidate full) today released the following statement on the circumstances surrounding the upcoming debate in los angeles, california: <p>"i have long stood with labor. if the cbs writers are still on strike, i will not cross the picket line for the upcoming presidential debate. </p><p>"supporting workers' rights is more important than anything i will say at the debate."</p></span>



